        Main area of studies: <b><%= @profile.main_area %></b> <br>
        Highest Academic title: <b><%= @profile.highest_academic %></b> <br>
        Country of Main Studies: <% @studycountry = Carmen::Country.coded(@profile.study_country) %> <b><%= @studycountry.name %></b> <br>
        <% if @profile.studies_other.present? %> Country of Main Studies Other:  <b><%= @profile.studies_other %></b> <br> <% end %> 
