        Years of Professional Experience: <b><%= @profile.years_experience %></b> <br>
        International Experience:  <b><%= @profile.international_experience %></b> <br>
        <hr>
        Company: <b><%= @profile.company %></b> <br>
         <% if @profile.company_other.present? %> Company Other: <b><%= @profile.company_other %></b>  <br> <% end %>
        Job Title: <b><%= @profile.company_title %></b> <br>
        Years in the company: <b><%= @profile.years_in_company %></b> &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;
        Number of direct subordinates: <b><%= @profile.number_subordinates %></b> <br>
        Job Function: <b><%= @profile.company_job_function %></b>  <br>
        Sector: <b><%= @profile.company_sector %></b> <br>
        Nationality: <b><%= @profile.company_nation %></b> <br>    
        Job Level: <b><%= @profile.job_level %></b> &emsp;&emsp;
        Level you report to: <b><%= @profile.reporting_level %></b> <br>
        <hr>
      </p>
      </div>
    <div style="margin-left: 40%; margin-top: 5%">
    <%= image_tag @profile.picture_url, :width => 150 %> </div>

  </div>
  

